com.android.server.am

Class BroadcastQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.android.server.am.BroadcastQueue

  • public class BroadcastQueue
extends java.lang.Object
    BROADCASTS We keep two broadcast queues and associated bookkeeping, one for those at foreground priority, and one for normal (background-priority) broadcasts.
